<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>My language learning</h1>

    <p>Start building your own study guide by creating an account.</p>

    <p>You'll be able to record words and phrases on the go in a language of your choice.</p>

    <p>Refer to them, revise them, or celebrate what you've learnt.</p>

    <h2>Create an account</h2>

    <form action="/start-language-learning" method="POST">
        <label for="username">Create a unique username</label>
        <br>
        <input type="text" name="username" id="username">
        <br>
        <label for="password">Create a password</label>
        <br>
        <input type="text" name="password" id="password">
        <br>
        <label for="confirmPassword">Enter your password again</label>
        <br>
        <input type="text" name="confirmPassword" id="confirmPassword">
        <br>
        <button type="submit">Sign up</button>
    </form>


    <p>Already have an account? <a href="/sign-in-language-learning">Sign in</a></p>

</body>
</html>